txt.en: The camp completely blocks the road south to Gondor. While there isn't a way to destroy the camp, destroying parts of the camp would make it easier for the Rohirrim to slip through the woods and for the Woses to not have to worry about Orcs travelling further into the forest.
Maudhúl Grak is a threat to both the Rohirrim and the Woses, and much be dealt with.
You have destroyed many trebuchets at Maudhúl Grak and caused a major setback for the Orcs camped here.
Maudhúl Grak is located in northern Taur Drúadan.\n\nYou should destroy trebuchets at Maudhúl Grak.
